data.description: Ceilings have been painted white and.....WOW!!!! Almost new home full of upgrades and move in ready. Landscaping, blinds, etc are done....all you need to do is move in and enjoy! Open floorplan is perfect for entertaining. Kitchen features quartz counters, a huge island with seating for 4, stainless steel appliances and opens to the dining area and living room with a gas fireplace. Upstairs you have split bedrooms with the loft between the primary bedroom and 3 additional, good-sized bedrooms. Five piece primary bath has an extra deep tub and walk in shower with glass door. Peaceful backyard with greenbelt to the rear and no neighbor to the right. Home is on a dead end street. Located near shopping, freeways, and 15 minutes to JBLM.
